Famicom Title: オールナイトニッポン スーパーマリオブラザーズ
Notes: Promotional FDS remix: SMB base with SMB2J imports; celeb reskins; stage edits.

Famicom Title: スーパーマリオブラザーズ2 (FDS)
Notes: FDS-only in JP; later came West via collections. Not cross-mapped to US NES.

Famicom Title: 帰ってきたマリオブラザーズ (FDS Disk Writer)
Notes: FDS Disk Writer update; ads, extra audio, tweaks; influenced PAL Classic Serie.

Famicom Title: いらっしゃい くるくるランド (Clu Clu Land D)
Notes: Later FDS update; VS.-derived. JP-only; seen in Animal Crossing as unlockable.
